article.description: — Aamer Muhammad scored 23 points and Myles Rigsby added 21 as Troy beat South Alabama 83-79 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Muhammad scores 23 as Troy takes down South Alabama 83-79
article.linkText: Muhammad scores 23 as Troy takes down South Alabama 83-79
article.story: TROY, Ala. -- — Aamer Muhammad scored 23 points and Myles Rigsby added 21 as Troy beat South Alabama 83-79 on Saturday night. Muhammad added eight rebounds for the Trojans (13-8, 7-2 Sun Belt Conference). Christyon Eugene finished with 11 points. The Jaguars (10-11, 3-6) were led by Tyrell Jones, who posted 19 points, six rebounds and three steals. Thomas Howell added 18 points for South Alabama. In addition, Marcus Millender finished with 16 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
